Class ActivityFactory

java.lang.Object
  it.unibz.pomodroid.factories.ActivityFactory

public class ActivityFactory
extends Object

A class that saves all information about tickets it into the database. Each ticket taken from TRAC is checked. If some information are empty, the class provides some auto-generated values.
